Text:
Wow the quality is surprisingly great for the size and the fact it's a telesinc from a camcorder in a cinema.  Whoever tweaked the colouring and audio and sharpened it up did a great job. 
Whoever animated that dragon must have had a dog very similar to mine too - made me laugh. ^_^

@kotique - I didn't have any of the audio problems you mentioned. 

@metalracket - I seriously doubt you'll get a 3D copy until this is released on DVD.  The security is MUCH tighter in 3D cinemas.
